  "interpretationBoundaries": [
    "The recorded upstream JSON and its SHA-256 are the only account-observation evidence used by this derivation; the generator performs no RPC or other network request.",
    "Browser and contract threshold rules are deterministic constants declared in the generator. The upstream account bytes supply observed XP values, not proof of those executable rules.",
    "Browser levels in keyOwners are chain-XP-only projections. Local behavior counters and browser-stored XP were not captured, so these values are not a claim about any player's complete visible effective level.",
    "The current Profile recovery projection models the reviewed refresh path: Precision, the Chunk-layout Smelting field, and Exploration come from Chunk Progress, while Forging comes from PlayerProfile. It does not read the Game/Smelting Progress account.",
